contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:04.080 --> 01:05.949
Very cute, Ian.

01:05.950 --> 01:07.505
The visibility is excellent,

01:07.506 --> 01:11.389
ventilation is greatly improved
from last year's model.

01:11.390 --> 01:13.359
Big step up.

01:13.360 --> 01:14.511
It better be.

01:14.512 --> 01:16.359
We don't need another
suffocation lawsuit.

01:16.360 --> 01:17.839
Thank God that happened on Purge.

01:17.840 --> 01:21.059
I think we should make a
push into the LGBTQ market.

01:21.060 --> 01:24.319
We'll look like we care,
earn a bunch of goodwill,

01:24.320 --> 01:25.349
make a tidy profit.

01:25.350 --> 01:26.979
Well, we do need more lifestyle reach.

01:26.980 --> 01:29.259
And focus groups reacted positively

01:29.260 --> 01:30.939
to the idea of a pride-themed mask.

01:30.940 --> 01:36.242
So we changed a few colors
on an old S.K.U. and voilÃ !

01:37.380 --> 01:38.780
I'd run with that.

01:38.786 --> 01:40.163
It shows we listen to our customers.

01:40.164 --> 01:42.719
Um, we should at least donate
a portion of the proceeds

01:42.720 --> 01:44.373
- to a relevant charity.
- Fine. Done.

01:44.374 --> 01:47.799
Jimmy, where are we at with the
inspired-by-true-events space?

01:47.800 --> 01:48.999
All the usuals...

01:49.000 --> 01:52.007
presidents, pop stars,
a lot of Hitler variations,

01:52.008 --> 01:54.419
but I would like to put
one more into production.

01:54.420 --> 01:55.739
Well, that'd be a hell of a rush job.

01:55.740 --> 01:58.306
It'll be worth it. Trust me.

01:59.320 --> 02:01.300
It's blowing up.

02:01.309 --> 02:02.679
The Campus Killer?

02:02.680 --> 02:05.779
We make Purge masks, not murder masks.

02:05.780 --> 02:07.909
We'd be promoting
an active serial killer.

02:07.910 --> 02:08.919
Yeah, you might be right.

02:08.919 --> 02:10.651
But our advertising
allowance has been slashed.

02:10.651 --> 02:11.789
With something like this,

02:11.790 --> 02:13.539
cable news does all the heavy lifting.

02:13.540 --> 02:17.359
I'm with Jimmy on this.
I mean, bad taste sells.

02:17.360 --> 02:19.559
Look how simple it is.

02:19.560 --> 02:21.299
Our margins will be huge.

02:21.300 --> 02:22.439
I'll call production.

02:22.440 --> 02:24.599
Let's get a run of these going ASAP.

02:24.600 --> 02:27.459
Hey, good work, kid.
We're gonna make a killing.

